--required context, found fragment
    1.'this' need to be replaced with 'activity.applicationContext' or with requireActivity().applicationContext
    2. replace 'this' with 'this.activity'


--id must not be null
    1. check whether you have attached to correct layout


--sometimes in fragment you may get an error 'this_this_id must not be null'
    1. So, just return a view in onCreateView
    2. Use onViewCreated function to access any this_this_id from corresponding XML


